What are the treatments for Testicular Cancer ?,"Key Points
                    - There are different types of treatment for patients with testicular cancer.    - Testicular tumors are divided into 3 groups, based on how well the tumors are expected to respond to treatment.          - Good Prognosis     - Intermediate Prognosis     - Poor Prognosi
